text:

However, I have a project that I believe may be of interest to the fund or funds with similar missions (i.e, long-term future).

Are there any other similar funds (other than OSF and EA) that award grants in a similar manner?

[1] https://ftxfuturefund.org/area-of-interest/artificial-intelligence/
